track_notes: This track shows the drive from NM 518 up FR 722 to a parking spot on a saddle just below Cerro Picacho, then the round trip hike on the continuation of the road to the Cerro Picacho summit and back to the parked vehicle. FR 722 was is good shape much of the way but had some significant rutted sections further up. A good 4WD could probably make it up most of the hike route.
I am sure there are better routes.  This is just what a Canadian would do with no prior knowledge of the area.  Locals will know better.
